title: Dell security advisory (AV25-292)
description: Between May 19 and 25, 2025, Dell published security advisories to address vulnerabilities in multiple products. Included were updates for the following products:
products: Dell Networking OS10  versions prior to 10.5.6.9
CloudBoost Virtual Appliance  versions prior to 19.12.0.1
solution: Review the references and apply the necessary updates.
